Help your team track orders, see whoâ€™s buying what products, discover year-to-date and year-over-year sales revenue, and more. The B2B Commerce Analytics template guides you through creating the app.

Available with CRM Analytics, which is available for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions. Also available in Developer Edition. Requires a CRM Analytics license and the Salesforce B2B Commerce (CloudCraze) managed package.

To create and manage the B2B Commerce Analytics app: Manage CRM Analytics Templated Apps
To use the B2B Commerce Analytics app: Use CRM Analytics Templated Apps and Manage Einstein Discovery

From the Analytics tab or Analytics Studio, click Create and then select App. Select the B2B Commerce Analytics template to open the guided flow. The guided flow checks that your org meets the minimum requirements. If your org meets the minimum requirements, click Looks good, next. Name and save your app.
